Press 1 to see the Menu
Press 2 to purchase a meal
Press 3 to Save & Exit
Press 4 to add a new food item
Press 5 to remove a food item
Press 6 to display the current coin balance
Press 7 to display the enhancements menu
Press 8 to exit the program
